https://kelee.one/Tool/Loon/Lpx/BoxJs.lpx, policy=Available, enabled=false
https://kelee.one/Tool/Loon/Lpx/Script-Hub.lpx, policy=Available, enabled=false
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sub-store-org/Sub-Store/master/config/Loon.plugin, policy=Available, enabled=false
